com.hamweather.aeris.tiles

Enum AerisPointData

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<AerisPointData>
      • com.hamweather.aeris.tiles.AerisPointData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AerisOverlay, Serializable, Comparable<AerisPointData>

    public enum AerisPointData
extends Enum<AerisPointData>
implements AerisOverlay
    Aeris point enum that helps setup each loading with the proper aeris query, proper handler and proper legend. Legends can be overridden by using their own drawable in the same name.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants

      Place holder for a none category to remove point data or not show any.
      STORM_CELLS

      Storm reports from the past 24 hours.
